},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"所以遲早連漢人都要入去再洗腦"},{"pid":"41dd449aae158a5b6ef3273cf9514cd62cd8c51c","tid":1027592,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8585334f653e3e5b476bb37ce5961091fe5f2f0","tid":1027592,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"Victor Gevers<br />\n&rlm; @0xDUDE<br />\n15h15 hours ago<br />\n<br />\nThis database records moving &quot;objects&quot; which are on the street or road to register if it's going to fast, going through a red light or jaywalking. Violations trigger an alarm event which makes a photo &amp; tries to do something (like a lookup) with the WeChat API using Hardware SDK.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4319ad482b2baae91bd0866b439f1a26bcd1a493","tid":1027592,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:20:15.000Z","msg":"日落帝蝈同德意志斯坦 : 中蝈5G好安全"},{"pid":"49708c4581839545e6b99649e4791970ccca0e91","tid":1027592,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"中國人出電話sim卡<br />\n係咪要 影相？"},{"pid":"65a1e0741518046b61fa8c69739bb9fc5541c751","tid":1027592,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49708c4581839545e6b99649e4791970ccca0e91","tid":1027592,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:52:15.000Z","msg":"中國人出電話sim卡<br />\n係咪要 影相？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T05:08:38.000Z","msg":"打機都要實名認證 視頻。"},{"pid":"5a97c5b72a6dc74df8cbd731dde36173145b17cd","tid":1027592